Package msp.simulator.satellite.assembly

Class SatelliteStates

  • java.lang.Object
    • msp.simulator.satellite.assembly.SatelliteStates

  • public class SatelliteStates
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible to store, maintain and provide tools to access the satellite state over the time in the simulation.

    Note that an OreKit Spacecraft state is immutable so any action on the satellite creates a new instance. Then this class focus on keeping up-to-date the right current state of the satellite in time.

    Author:
    Florian CHAUBEYRE
    See Also:
    SpacecraftState
